I've been trying to
wake you up since 7:00.

00:09.271 --> 00:10.897
Mm. I don't wanna get up.

00:10.898 --> 00:12.473
All right.

00:12.474 --> 00:15.728
Then I'm coming in. Oh!

00:16.101 --> 00:17.846
Oh, not now. I have a headache.

00:17.847 --> 00:19.086
You have a headache?

00:19.087 --> 00:20.781
- Yeah. 
- Can't you wait till we're married

00:20.782 --> 00:22.425
For you to bust that one out?

00:22.426 --> 00:25.425
Some people get real
headaches. Oh, really?

00:25.426 --> 00:28.494
I don't know. Maybe
I still have the flu.

00:29.087 --> 00:31.442
You've been in bed for a week.

00:31.443 --> 00:33.005
Do you want to skip my
mom's benefit tonight?

00:33.006 --> 00:34.903
No. God, no.I need to
get outta the house.

00:34.904 --> 00:36.530
I'm so bored.

00:36.531 --> 00:38.826
Well, you wanna know
what dr. Walker thinks?

00:38.827 --> 00:40.852
No. Come on. I'm taking
clinical diagnosis.

00:40.853 --> 00:45.426
Let me try. Let me try. All right.

00:45.427 --> 00:48.126
Uh... No fever.

00:48.127 --> 00:51.193
Could it be ojai food poisoning?

00:51.194 --> 00:54.025
Or idiopathic
wedding-plan-itis?

00:54.026 --> 00:55.804
Wedding-plan-itis?
Mm-hmm.

00:55.805 --> 00:58.672
Don't you have to get
to school or something?

00:58.673 --> 01:00.792
Oh, I do.

01:00.793 --> 01:02.723
I love you. All right.

01:02.724 --> 01:05.197
Look, if you don't feel
better, call me, all right?

01:05.197 --> 01:07.842
Get up.

01:08.198 --> 01:10.672
They cut our line of
credit in half? Why?

01:10.673 --> 01:12.319
Because everything
else in the neighborhood

01:12.320 --> 01:13.082
Is selling for less...

01:13.083 --> 01:14.573
So our place is less valuable.

01:14.574 --> 01:17.234
God, I hate banks. All
they care about is money.

01:17.235 --> 01:18.353
How much did they leave us?

01:18.354 --> 01:21.743
Uh, $50,000, which is not
enough to pay for this baby.

01:21.744 --> 01:23.133
Just getting michelle
approved as our surrogate

01:23.134 --> 01:25.458
And the screening alone
was close to 5 grand.

01:25.459 --> 01:27.848
Well, you know, fine.
I will--I'll cater more.

01:27.849 --> 01:30.085
Cater? We're talking $50,000.

01:30.086 --> 01:31.610
Well, I'll cater a lot if I have to.

01:31.611 --> 01:34.153
Well, what am I supposed to do,
steal campaign contributions?

01:34.154 --> 01:36.715
It'd be money better spent.
Oh, if you think robert's bad,

01:36.716 --> 01:39.020
Wait till you see this
nut job barry henderson

01:39.021 --> 01:40.952
Who's entering the primary today.

01:40.953 --> 01:43.495
He'd cut our line of
credit just for being gay.

01:43.496 --> 01:44.868
Well, what are we supposed to do?

01:44.869 --> 01:46.193
We've come this far. I
don't want to give up just--

01:46.194 --> 01:48.599
I will talk to another bank
and I will get us this loan.

01:48.600 --> 01:49.955
I promise.

01:49.956 --> 01:52.955
Ugh. I gotta run. My phone's
been buzzing all morning

01:52.956 --> 01:56.108
'Cause of this henderson
dude. Did you just say "dude"?

01:56.109 --> 01:57.193
Oh, yeah. Sorry.

01:59.194 --> 02:01.569
Call the police! There's
an insane man outside!

02:01.570 --> 02:03.721
No, kevin, kevin, that's
kluve the crusader. Who?!

02:03.722 --> 02:06.348
That's my father wearing his
kluve the crusader costume.

02:06.349 --> 02:07.281
Kluve?

02:07.282 --> 02:09.721
From planet kluven.

02:09.722 --> 02:13.494
Just let him in.

02:18.420 --> 02:20.487
Hi, wally. Hi, kevin.

02:20.488 --> 02:23.894
Sorry. Didn't mean to scare ya.

02:23.895 --> 02:25.592
Hi, dad.

02:25.593 --> 02:26.812
Hi, son.

02:26.813 --> 02:30.159
Wow. Hey, I-I see the--
the costume still fits.

02:30.160 --> 02:31.965
There's a comic convention in town,

02:31.966 --> 02:34.558
So I thought I'd get it
out of the mothballs and go.

02:34.559 --> 02:36.456
It was kind of a last-minute thing.

02:36.457 --> 02:38.219
Where's, uh, where's mom?

02:38.220 --> 02:40.826
Um, she didn't want to come.

02:40.827 --> 02:43.476
Oh, yeah. Well, she never
loved kluve the way we did.

02:43.477 --> 02:47.103
No, she didn't. But, uh...

02:47.104 --> 02:48.951
Scotty...

02:48.952 --> 02:52.427
Your mother left me.

02:55.260 --> 02:56.191
- Mom? 
- Yeah.

02:56.192 --> 02:58.937
Have you seen my keys? I-I
let evan play with them,

02:58.938 --> 03:00.886
And then they just seem to migrate.

03:00.887 --> 03:04.228
Oh, thank you. And where my
last quarter contribution report

03:04.229 --> 03:07.160
Has migrated to, I do not know.

03:07.161 --> 03:09.567
Oh, well, you can't blame evan for that.

03:09.568 --> 03:12.593
Oh! Ooh, I'm gonna be late
for my meeting at the center

03:12.594 --> 03:14.593
About tonight's benefit.

03:14.594 --> 03:16.720
Oh, could I have picked

03:16.721 --> 03:19.248
A worse time to be raising money?

03:19.249 --> 03:20.994
Mom, did you know that perfectionists

03:20.995 --> 03:23.028
Have far more stress and conflict

03:23.029 --> 03:24.299
In their lives than--
you're telling me.

03:24.300 --> 03:25.706
I have convinced
myself--

03:25.707 --> 03:27.028
no one's coming tonight, no one.

03:27.029 --> 03:28.452
Mom, you need to lose the stress.

03:28.453 --> 03:31.167
The stress is going to deplete
your adrenaline reserves.

03:31.168 --> 03:32.251
Who needs adrenaline?

03:32.252 --> 03:33.878
I'm practically spinning like a top.

03:33.879 --> 03:36.082
Mom, the benefit is
gonna be great, okay?

03:36.083 --> 03:40.710
Now relax. Okay, now I will
be home in a couple of hours.

03:41.661 --> 03:45.361
Kitty? Kitty?

03:46.494 --> 03:47.322
Kitty?

03:47.323 --> 03:49.119
Um, don't you have your appointment

03:49.120 --> 03:51.898
With dr. Avadon today? Oh,
you know what? I canceled it.

03:51.899 --> 03:52.746
I--you know,
I just--

03:52.747 --> 03:54.831
I really want something
new for the benefit,

03:54.832 --> 03:56.342
So I'm gonna go shopping.

03:56.343 --> 03:58.359
Oh, well, what day did
you reschedule it for?

03:58.360 --> 03:59.461
Maybe I could go with you.

03:59.462 --> 04:00.817
You don't have to worry about it.

04:00.818 --> 04:03.495
Besides, you know, I'm just not so keen

04:03.496 --> 04:05.732
On dr. Avadon anymore.

04:05.733 --> 04:07.224
What--what
did she do?

04:07.225 --> 04:09.295
Do you want to find another doctor?

04:09.296 --> 04:10.769
No, no, no, it's not
that. She's--she's great.

04:10.770 --> 04:14.028
It's just, um...

04:14.029 --> 04:18.413
Well, I'm--I'm thinking
about some alternatives

04:18.414 --> 04:21.416
Instead of doing any more chemo.

04:21.993 --> 04:24.145
What?

04:24.146 --> 04:26.128
Are you insane? What
are you talking about?

04:26.129 --> 04:29.721
Mother, I... I really wish
you wouldn't freak out.

04:29.722 --> 04:31.959
Well, how do you expect me to react?

04:31.960 --> 04:33.755
Stopping chemo at this time

04:33.756 --> 04:35.504
Would be the worst
possible thing you could do.

04:35.505 --> 04:36.555
How do you know?

04:36.556 --> 04:38.690
Kitty, stop. Please.
You're frightening me.

04:38.691 --> 04:40.063
Before you say another word, mom,

04:40.064 --> 04:41.487
Remember that you weren't
the one sitting there

04:41.488 --> 04:43.895
With a bag full of poison
dripping into your arm,

04:43.896 --> 04:46.640
Shivering and--and trying
to get warm from the chills.

04:46.641 --> 04:47.862
And you weren't the one

04:47.863 --> 04:49.593
who was so jacked up on prednisone

04:49.594 --> 04:51.196
That you got up at 3:00 in the morning

04:51.197 --> 04:53.513
- And cleaned up the kitchen. 
- You were up all night?

04:53.514 --> 04:56.029
I didn't know that.

04:57.292 --> 04:59.529
Well, that's because you were sleeping.

04:59.530 --> 05:01.783
Why didn't you tell me any of this?

05:01.784 --> 05:03.084
Did you tell robert?

05:03.085 --> 05:05.941
No, mom. It doesn't make any difference.

05:05.942 --> 05:06.878
Yes, it does.

05:06.879 --> 05:08.878
We need to know what
you're going through

05:08.879 --> 05:11.395
- So we can help you. 
- Mom, you don't get it.

05:11.396 --> 05:16.163
The only one that can
help me now... Is me.

05:16.164 --> 05:19.211
That's not true,
kitty. That's not--

05:19.212 --> 05:21.656
Where are you going?

05:21.974 --> 05:22.847
Kitty?

