quit chemo at some point.

15:10.208 --> 15:13.335
And almost everyone goes back.

15:14.208 --> 15:17.731
I just want kitty to be
realistic about all of this.

15:17.732 --> 15:19.128
Well, what's realistic?

15:19.129 --> 15:20.810
