20:10.897 --> 20:12.175
No, remember your date?

20:12.176 --> 20:14.039
He hugged you, and they popped out?

20:14.040 --> 20:15.864
- Oh, no, no, stop, stop.
- You were so embarrassed.

20:15.865 --> 20:16.836
Okay, okay, stop.

20:16.837 --> 20:17.943
I'm not gonna think
about that. That I--

20:17.944 --> 20:20.070
That is too much negative energy.

20:20.071 --> 20:23.721
I'm just--i-I don't remember
going to those dances.

20:23.722 --> 20:28.372
All I remember is
getting ready with you.

20:28.373 --> 20:32.086
Well, that was the only fun part.

20:32.087 --> 20:33.673
And, sarah...

20:33.674 --> 20:37.437
Thank you so much for
doing this with me.

20:40.690 --> 20:42.197
Let's hope that, um...

20:42.198 --> 20:44.609
This is the only thing
you remember when,

20:44.610 --> 20:47.870
